programme and showed rather poor performance scoring only  points out of  for frontal impact the passenger compartment became unstable in the crash test it was determined that there was an unacceptable high risk of chest injury during side impact crash as a result the car would not meet the minimum legal requirement in  the swedish insurance company folksam rates the stgen accent as one of the safest cars in its weight class galleryedit prefacelift hyundai excel door australia prefacelift hyundai excel sedan australia facelift hyundai excel sedan australia facelift hyundai excel sedan australia facelift hyundai excel door australia kia qianlima  kia qianlima  second generation lc –edit second generation lc overview also called dodge verna mexico giad accent sudan hyundai accent admire hyundai accent verna hyundai brio hyundai avega hyundai verna hyundai verna viva hyundai accent gyro hyundai verna super taxi hyundai super pony hyundai accent excecutive production – south korea – india – russia assembly ulsan south korea chennai india hyundai motor india i̇zmit turkey hyundai assan taganrog russia tagaz cairo egypt ghabbour group khartoum sudan giad kerman iran rvmco bekasi indonesia hyundai indonesia body and chassis body style door sedan  and door hatchback platform hyundaikia tb related hyundai getz powertrain engine  l alpha i gasoline  l alpha i gasoline  l alpha i gasoline  l u i diesel transmission speed automatic speed manual dimensions wheelbase  mm  in length  mm  in – sedan  mm  in – sedan  mm  in hatchback width  mm  in –  mm  in – height  mm  in curb weight – lb – kg the redesigned  accent lc sported a more angular body and increased dimensions it received a minor facelift in  and was given the model code lc when the accent sedan underwent a  redesign the hatchback continued on sale during  only in canada since the hatchback skipped the  model year for the united states but for korea it was the first model with the new nameplate verna the accent got new 