et on  february  the new verna midsized sedan gets changes to both styling and mechanism the updated hyundai verna gets new front fascia apart from the same petrol and diesel engine versions the fourspeed automatic gearbox is likely to be offered in the upcoming model however the maker might also introduce the sixspeed automatic gearbox according to motorbeam hyundai has started testing the fifth generation verna and the company will launch the new model in the indian market in the second half of  indonesiaedit in indonesia the accent hatchback is sold as the grand avega the car made its debut at the  indonesia international motor show and is assembled locally the grand avega is equipped with two engines and three transmissions a  l petrol ps gamma engine with  at or  mt and a  l petrol ps kappa engine with  mt mexicoedit in mexico it was marketed as dodge verna from  a  and as dodge attitude from  a  until may  after hyundais arrival in the country forcing dodge to give the name attitude to the mitsubishi attrage it is unknown if the car will be reintroduced as the hyundai accent in  or until the cars next redesign in  return with your name true hyundai accent as model  philippinesedit in the philippines the third generation mc sedan was introduced and made available in  exclusively with a  litre dfa common rail direct injection crdi turbodiesel with vgt with hp and nm with a  mt a number of units saw action in the taxi industry because of fuel efficiency coupled with cheaper diesel fuel costs in  came the rb model in both sedan and hatchback platforms the sedan was powered by a ps gamma engine with a  at or  mt some of first batch of rb models were dogged by knocking issues when using  and below octane fuel a second iteration was introduced in  with a ps kappa engine with  mt or  at and a  litre dfb common rail direct injection turbodiesel with ps and nm in mt or at variants in  the diesel variant comes with an electronic vgt in both  mt and  speed dual clutch aut